article.description: — Kaleb Higgins scored 21 points to help Cal State Bakersfield defeat Cal Poly 68-56 on Saturday night, handing the Mustangs their 18th loss in a row.
article.headline: Cal State Bakersfield beats Cal Poly 68-56, hands Mustangs 18th straight defeat
article.linkText: Cal State Bakersfield beats Cal Poly 68-56, hands Mustangs 18th straight defeat
article.story: SAN LUIS OBISPO, Calif. -- — Kaleb Higgins scored 21 points to help Cal State Bakersfield defeat Cal Poly 68-56 on Saturday night, handing the Mustangs their 18th loss in a row. Higgins added seven rebounds for the Roadrunners (13-17, 8-11 Big West Conference). Dalph Panopio had 10 points and Fidelis Okereke hit three 3-pointers and scored nine. Kobe Sanders had 24 points and six rebounds to pace the Mustangs (4-26, 0-18). Justin Page added nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
